WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.470 --> 00:00:03.442
Endi keling qanday qilib raqamlar 
faoliyatini sozlab, for siklini 

00:00:03.442 --> 00:00:05.530
while sikli o‘rniga so‘zlar
 bo‘ylab harakatlanishga 
3
00:00:05,530 --&gt; 00:00:09,840
ishlatishni o‘ylab ko‘ramiz.

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:13.960
Xo‘sh, hozircha while siklida
 bizda indeks joylashuvi, shart,

00:00:13.960 --> 00:00:18.600
va yangilash o‘zgaruvchisi 
har xil satrlarda mavjud.

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:21.240
Lekin yodingizda bo‘lsa, for siklida
 biz hammasini bitta satrda yozamiz.

00:00:22.340 --> 00:00:24.231
Endi men davom etaman, va shu uchta
qismni o‘chirib tashlayman.

00:00:24.231 --> 00:00:30.541
[AUDIO YO‘Q]

00:00:30.541 --> 00:00:34.719
Xo‘sh, bu yerda biz for kalit so‘zi 
bilan boshladik va while siklidagi 

00:00:34.719 --> 00:00:39.378
uchta qismni, ya’ni boshlang‘ich holat, 
takrorlash sharti va takrorlash 

00:00:39.378 --> 00:00:42.960
qadamini yangilashni bitta 
satrga birlashtiramiz.

00:00:44.250 --> 00:00:48.080
Shunday qilib, har bir siklda bajarish kerak
 bo‘lgan vazifa o‘zgarmaydi,

00:00:48.080 --> 00:00:50.360
shuning uchun biz tana qismini o‘zgartirmaymiz. 

00:00:50.360 --> 00:00:53.770
Mana bu esa for sikli raqamlar 
faoliyatida qo‘llanganining oxirgi versiyasi 

00:00:53.770 --> 00:00:54.460
qanday ko‘rinishga kelishi.

